// 23A Final
// goldrush_revival_v2
// BOTH TEAMS should HAVE About 50% CHANCE TO DECIDE THE TANK PATH
// BOTH TEAMS should HAVE About 50 % CHANCE TO WIN THE MAP  
// These bot files ORIGINALLY converted from fa_goldrush_b1.gm
// BUT THEY ARE MAJORLY UPGRADED & UPDATED 23A Final release
// BOTS FINISHED C4W 02.27.2025
// BATTERY IS NOT DESTRUCTABLE, IT CAN NOT BE DAMAGED.
// ALL versions of this map have a GLITCH, these bot files are set to intentionally avoid the GLITCH.
// Bots will not cause the Glitch totally alone, but with Humans involved it can happen.
// HUMANS should NOT STEAL the TANK, ONLY bots should build to STEAL the Tank or THe Glitch may happen.
// ALL versions of this map not just this version.
//  C4W - Enjoy!
// 
//  
// 
//  
//	Who                  	When		What
